      "raw_text": "The Northern Pacific railway\nannounces dates for special rates\nto eastern points as follows: July\n2 and 3, August 7, and 8, Septem.\nDer s and 10, st. Paul, Omoha or\nKansas City and return, $3.50; St\nLouis and return, $4,000; Chicago\nand return, $4,000.\n\n\nC. A. MITCHELL. G. A."
    }
